POWER
  Show nation power rankings across all active countries.

SYNTAX
  power
  powe

DESCRIPTION
  Displays a ranking of all active nations by military power.
  The power score is calculated from:
    - Military strength (troops, ships, planes, land units)
    - Sector count and efficiency
    - Tech and research levels
    - Treasury size

  This gives you an overview of the competitive landscape and helps
  gauge relative strength before diplomacy or war.

  Nations marked as 'deity' (country 0) are not shown.
  Your own country is highlighted in the list.

EXAMPLE
  power                     see all nations ranked by power

SEE ALSO
  nation  relations  report  census
